<HEAD>Former President Calls for Pacific Free Trade Zone</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By ELAINE KURTENBACH</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>OSAKA, Japan (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
